</hgroup><div class="metabar"><div class="metabar-pad"><em>By <span class="author vcard sc"><span class="fn"><a href="http://www.atab.org.uk/author/atab-editor/" title="Posts by ATAB Editor" rel="author">ATAB Editor</a></span></span> On <time class="date time published updated sc" datetime="2013-09-19T10:47:00+00:00">September 19, 2013</time>  &middot; <span class="post-comments sc"><a href="http://www.atab.org.uk/2013/09/a-sea-change-in-st-barts/#wp-comments"><span vanilla-identifier="37285">Add Comment</span></a></span> &middot; In <span class="categories sc"><a href="http://www.atab.org.uk/category/air-travel-news/" title="View all posts in Air Travel News" rel="category tag">Air Travel News</a></span>  </em></div></div></section> </section></section><div class="entry_wrap fix"><div class="entry_content"><p>In winter, St Barts is an ostentatious celebrity playground, but island life becomes far more refined during April&#8217;s Les Voiles de Saint-Barth regatta.<img width='1' height='1' src='http://www.atab.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/mf775.gif' border='0' />
